commentPostTextItems.html: Thanks for joining us today. Please do join me for the game on Tuesday. Till then it's a good night from me and all of us here

Afghanistan goes 2 nil up with a thumping 54 run win. Mire and PJ Moor provided strong foundation at the top with Mire the chief destroyer amassing almost a run-a-ball 54. that was followed by 2 quick wickets which pegged Zimbabwe back but Ervine and Burl controlled the middle innings somewhat with a 54 run fourth wicket and then Zimbabwe lost 6 wicket for 39 runs from there. Spinners R Khan and M Nabi grabbed 3 wickets apiece, G Naib and A Hamza got 2 each to scuttle Zimbabwe for 184 inside 42.1 overs

milestones.description: Mohammad Nabi has become the top wicket-taker for AFG in ODIs with 73 wickets, going past Dawlat Zadran's 70
Dawlat Zadran has broken the record for most ducks (5) in ODIs for AFG, going past Asghar Afghan's 5

stories.title: Afghanistan go 2-0 up after spinners run through Zimbabwe
stories.subTitle: Zimbabwe v Afghanistan, 2nd ODI, Harare
stories.seoTitle: Afghanistan go 2-0 up after spinners run through Zimbabwe
stories.summary: Afghanistan went 2-0 up in the five-match ODI series against Zimbabwe after their bowlers ran through the hosts' batting to complete a 54-run win
